jSimPack

Interface FutureEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTimer, PrintDataEvent, PrintEvent, ScheduleOtherEvent, SystemTimer, Timer

    public interface FutureEventListener
    Receives notification when events are released from a FutureEventList.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void eventReleased(java.lang.Object data)
      Invoked when an event is released from a FutureEventList.

    • Method Detail

      • eventReleased

        void eventReleased(java.lang.Object data)
        Invoked when an event is released from a FutureEventList. The argument is whatever was passed as the data parameter when jSimPack.FutureEventList#schedule(FutureEventListener, long, Object) was called to register this event.
